-- Korean Air Mulling Czech Airlines Bid, Lidove Says
-- B y   L a d k a   B a u e r o v a
-- 2012-12-03T11:10:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-03/korean-air-interested-in-buying-czech-airlines-lidove-says.html
(Corrects to show that Korean Air’s discussions are
internal, not with Czech Airlines in first paragraph).  Korean Air Lines Co. (003490)  Ltd. is holding
internal discussions on whether to bid for Ceske Aerolinie AS,
the Czech money-losing state carrier, Lidove Noviny reported,
citing the South Korean airline’s spokesman Choi Kibeom.  No decision on the sale has been made yet, according to the
newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladka Bauerova in Prague at 
 lbauerova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  